Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.17,0:00:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個目標是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.75,0:00:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭克·科拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算把他的底細查清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要動用那些來路不明的傢伙們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派遣她們是已經決定了的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要大幹一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.76,0:00:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了彰顯我們的存在  這也是必要的措施
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們的力量將成為烈火  將地獄燃燒至盡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.19,0:00:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並在那裡開墾我們的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.16,0:01:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦傷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.39,0:01:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺戮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了生存而…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺戮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不逃跑的話就會被幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法從那黑色的瞳孔逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然逃不掉  就只好反殺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不殺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會被殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.62,0:04:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道自己的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日語?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行背包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一個日本的旅行者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼想不起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些襲擊我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別一個人行動啊  克勞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則那些保鏢都請來幹什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想坐坐我的車嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  只是去看看那邊的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能把全部事情都交給那個男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個臭蛇男  現在一定在用極品玩具玩著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  令人作嘔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他對組織的貢獻很高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是馬格維雅他們看好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了達到目的  不惜任何手段
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是Inferno的作風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  克勞  你這獨木橋也走得太過了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼情況就聯絡我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:05:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠你了啊  利茲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是她不那樣駕駛就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況判斷率074
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺醒值087
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來幾分鐘就已經到達了這種數值  這真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該說過了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是奇才
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將會墮入地獄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  也許已經在地獄了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那感知能力是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是動物的本質啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是存在於理性中的野性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是還不夠  還沒達到我追求的領域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候出場了  Phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  別幹過火了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  Master
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.39,0:08:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想死的話就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力以赴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心理的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能與之對抗的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有自己體內的生存本能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依靠道德和溫柔這類東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為自己的安全會被保障
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種便是放棄了生的懦弱的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這已變成日常的世上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:09:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是異類  正討厭著這樣的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是瑪秋奈小姐嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是知道您要來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得結果快出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那請到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會盯著我來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連這理由也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪裡也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.76,0:09:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是誰也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡也去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然逃不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.72,0:10:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論你還是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不殺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會被殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請好好地看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力以赴吧  如果你還不想死的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管過去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是未來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連生命也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既便如此  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.55,0:11:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們該去什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連自己從哪來的都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連回憶都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做才能獲得自由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立在殺人之上的自由又算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我  求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪裡  我是…我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zwei
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Ein  你是Zwei
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}註：Ein是德語裡「1」的意思；Zwei是德語裡「2」的意思。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zwei…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從今天開始就叫Zwei
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zwei…這是什麼…意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:15:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我  我就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何  您不認為這是個非常傑出的人才嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這還真是驚人的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這少年既沒接受過訓練  也不懂戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅是依靠本能就採取了那樣的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還一時超越了Ein
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是狼狽  Phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還擁有著陷入生死關頭時  才會展示出來的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他簡直就是為了加入Inferno而誕生的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  他願意接受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有不願意出世的蛋  也沒有不願意萌芽的種
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是意願的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你擅長的洗腦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:16:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常完美  用催眠和藥物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只將與他身份有關的記憶封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您理解  瑪秋奈小姐  這是對他的慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他太過不幸的碰巧在現場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來他是應該被除掉的目擊者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想給他一個過上有意義的人生的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨自的旅行者  而且是日本人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可很麻煩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.30,0:16:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有人能查到他的行蹤  保密作業萬無一失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  賽斯·瑪斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這少年就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ein和Zwei
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:17:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能好好想一下學生的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為你還能指使我到什麼時候呢  小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一個女人  Ein
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.99,0:17:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是第二個男人  Zwei
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經完事了  Ein
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到你的崗位上去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  Master
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是沒有歸宿的亡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.22,0:17:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有自我的Phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的人怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  已經休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大白天就休息？這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom  Inferno最強的暗殺者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賜予組織最強狙擊手的稱號
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的最高傑作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有他也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得太過火了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那混蛋的組織也完蛋了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來在洛杉磯的5個組織中的2個就已經被滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位  從此以後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用我們的雙手創造時代
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創造Inferno的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有歸宿的亡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有自我的Phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.95,0:23:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回預告  訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.54,0:23:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經只能依靠殺人而存在
